        "TextSection": {
            "TextSectionType": "Definition",
            "Contents": "Olivopontocerebellar atrophy-deafness syndrome is characterised by infancy-onset olivopontocerebellar atrophy sensorineural deafness and speech impairment. It has been described in less than 15 children. Most cases were sporadic but autosomal recessive inheritance was suggested in three cases."
        },
